Articles.Content:
This mission was full of firsts for me; it included the first large interplanetary craft I have ever completed and flown, my first landing of an aircraft on another planet or moon, my first manned Jool expedition and my first Laythe landing. Surprisingly, this was also my first attempt at a Laythe mission. 

> [Javascript is disabled. View full album](//imgur.com/a/xdB9X)

The crew is now awaiting the Jool-Kerbin launch window.
